{{For|BSTc|Stria terminalis}} {{Infobox university | name = Bayan College of Science and Technology (BSTC) | native_name = <big>'''كلية البيان للعلوم والتكنولوجيا'''</big> | image_name = | image_size = | image_alt = | caption = | latin_name = | motto = | motto_lang = | mottoeng = | established = {{Start date|1997}} | closed = | type = [[Private university|Private]] | affiliation = | endowment = | officer_in_charge = | chairman = [[Yassin Homaida]] | chancellor = | president = | vice-president = | superintendent = | provost = | vice_chancellor = | rector = | principal = | dean = [[Jafar Mohammed Bashir]] | director = | head_label = | head = | academic_staff = | administrative_staff = | students = | undergrad = | postgrad = | doctoral = | other = | city = [[Khartoum]] | state = [[Khartoum]] | province = | country = [[Sudan]] | coor = {{Coord|15|35|57|N|32|30|34|E|display=title}} | campus = | former_names = | free_label = | free = | colors = | colours = | athletics = | sports = | nickname = | mascot = | affiliations = | website = {{URL|http://www.bayantech.edu}} | logo = | footnotes = }}
The '''Bayan College for Science & Technology''' ([[Arabic]]:كلية البيان للعلوم و التكنلوجيا ) is an educational institution based in the city of [[Khartoum]], [[Sudan]]. It was established in 1997 and admitted the first students in 1998.
The college offers diplomas in Construction Engineering and Construction, [[Information Technology]] and Engineering of medical equipment. It offers bachelor's degrees in Computer Science, Information Systems and Electronic Engineering.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bayantech.edu/ |title=Home |publisher=Bayan College of Science & Technology |accessdate=2011-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110920215435/http://www.bayantech.edu/ |archivedate=2011-09-20 |df= }}</ref> The college is a member of the Sudanese University Libraries Consortium.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eifl.net/system/files/201105/sudanese_university_libraries_consortium.pdf |title=Sudanese University Libraries Consortium members |accessdate=2011-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111221170233/http://www.eifl.net/system/files/201105/sudanese_university_libraries_consortium.pdf |archivedate=2011-12-21 |df= }}</ref>
